Package io.cui.core.uimodel.result

Class ResultOptional<T extends Serializable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.cui.core.uimodel.result.ResultObject<Optional<T>>
      • io.cui.core.uimodel.result.ResultOptional<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - identifying the type of the result
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    public class ResultOptional<T extends Serializable>
extends ResultObject<Optional<T>>
    A ResultObject that can store results that are not mandatory from the domain context. E.g. the parent of a node object that can also be a root node without a parent. To allow serialization the result will be stored as nullable object and transformed in an Optional for ResultObject.getResult().
